## Question

```json
{
  "id": 1001,
  "emoji": "🐱☕",
  "answer": "猫咖",
  "aliases": [
    "猫咪咖啡馆"
  ],
  "hint": "一种店铺",
  "difficulty": 2,
  "category": "名词",
  "score": 100
}
```

